summary: An Ordinance authorizing a refund of Three and 30/100 ($3.30) dollars out of 6th Avenue North Fund District No. 408, Ordinance No. 6823 in favor of W. T. Graham, which amount represents an excess paid into said Fund at time of paying 5th installment of amount assessed against, East 1/2 of Lot 6, Block 51 Replat of Blocks 44 to 53 Mercer's 2nd Addition as evidenced by Treasure's Receipt No. License-4959, February 21st, 1907.
